<header>
	In what order do you think the candidate should perform these tasks after being given the discussion topic? Choose the right order.
</header>
	
<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/LC_SP_004.JPG" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  <p align="left"><b>In Part 2 of the IELTS Speaking Module you will be given a topic, time to think and make notes, then one to two minutes to talk.</b>Use your time to:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>be clear about instructions</li>
    <li>get your ideas in a logical order</li>
    <li>have enough materials to speak until the examiner stops you</li>
  </ol>
  <p align="left">
    <b>In what order should you perform these tasks in Part 2 of the Speaking Module?</b>
    <g id="t1">A.  Think Speak Write Read</g>
    <g id="t2">B.  Think Read Speak Write</g>
    <g id="t3">C.  Write Read Speak Think</g>
    <g id="t4">D.  Write Speak Read Think</g>
    <g id="t5">E.  Read Write Think Speak</g>
    <g id="t6">F.  Read Think Write Speak</g>
    <g id="t7">G.  Speak Think Read Write</g>
    <g id="t8">H.  Speak Write Think Read</g>
  </p>
</section>

